Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.29,0:00:10.16,D,,0,0,0,,We're in a time of peace
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.14,0:00:12.89,D,,0,0,0,,Shows power like this
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.89,0:00:14.86,D,,0,0,0,,are just going to give off the wrong impression
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.86,0:00:18.16,D,,0,0,0,,You honestly believe your children can win a war?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.46,0:00:20.43,D,,0,0,0,,I hope they never have to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:23.40,D,,0,0,0,,I don't understand how everyone can be so calm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.10,0:00:25.60,D,,0,0,0,,You're still thinking about Torchwick?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.60,0:00:27.97,D,,0,0,0,,Torchwick, the White Fang, all of it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.97,0:00:30.87,D,,0,0,0,,Something big is happening and no one is doing anything about it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.87,0:00:32.04,D,,0,0,0,,We're not ready
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.04,0:00:33.65,D,,0,0,0,,And we may never be ready
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.65,0:00:37.11,D,,0,0,0,,Our enemies aren't just gonna sit around and wait for graduation day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.11,0:00:40.29,D,,0,0,0,,They're out there somewhere, planning their next move
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.29,0:00:43.00,D,,0,0,0,,And none of us know what it is, but it's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.00,0:00:44.39,D,,0,0,0,,Have a little faith
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.39,0:00:47.76,D,,0,0,0,,You'll know what you need when you need to know
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.76,0:00:49.66,D,,0,0,0,,Our second semester's going to be great
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.66,0:00:51.96,D,,0,0,0,,But classes start back up tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.96,0:00:55.83,D,,0,0,0,,Which is why I've taken the time to schedule a series wonderful events for us today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.83,0:00:56.90,D,,0,0,0,,This ought to be good
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.07,0:01:00.31,D,,0,0,0,,They're supposed to be the defenders of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.31,0:01:01.57,D,,0,0,0,,And they will be
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.57,0:01:04.11,D,,0,0,0,,But right now they're still children
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.14,0:01:07.31,D,,0,0,0,,So why not let them play the part
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.91,0:01:10.28,D,,0,0,0,,It isn't the role they'll have forever
